    {% call components.section("Usage") -%}

        <!--<h3>Use case detail (multiple examples)</h3>-->

        <p>Use popovers for on-page form field labels, titles, links, headings, tables, and column headings. A visual cue is required to trigger a popover, and the user must engage with the trigger to activate the popover. The user must close the popover or engage with the additional link provided to exit an active popover.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Anticipating and answering a user question.</li>
                <li>Explaining unfamiliar terms</li>
                <li>When providing context around a task</li>
            </ul>

